c: 74
v: 28
t: "sadkhlh jhnm; kay yaslaa hrraha wayahtariq binaraha wama 'aealamuk ay shay' jahnam? la tubqi lhmana wala tatrak ezmana 'iilaa 'ahraqatahu, mghyirt lilbasharati, mswwidt liljuludi, muharaqatan laha, yali 'amriha wayatasalat ealaa 'ahliha bialeadhab tset eshr mlkana min alzabaniat al'ashda'"